name: sagara
description:
I'm a microscopic part of the universe, which in a flick of a finger, can vanish with no flavor. 

There is no reason to be tall, because waterfalls, river currents, and mountain winds can sweep you away at any time.

There was no reason to worry too much, because the valleys and mountains that accepted fate with airy chest turned out to hold incredible beauty. 

Enjoy it, while you can.
